data.description: Absolutely Stunning 3 BDRM/2 Bath, fireplace home w/ screened in lanai, located in a nice cul de sac on a nice large lot. Enjoy the outdoors without the bugs on the screened in rear porch with sliding glass doors. This home has been cared for and is in move in ready condition. This location will not be far from the new SR 23 coming through the area, making the trip to Jacksonville or St Augustine much faster. Several schools are within walking distance and grocery stores and restaurants are close by.
